[center]DESCRIPTION:[/center]

This is my first ENB Series preset. So go easy on me guys.
If you\'re not familiar with Boris Vorontsov\'s ENBSeries, visit http://enbdev.com/

Screenshots with SSAO disabled
Also, enbseries.ini in the rar are with SSAO disabled too.

I\'m afraid there is not much to tell, just try it yourself.
Also, if you tried and liked, please Endorse this file!

Thanks.


[center]TO INSTALL :[/center]
extract all the file to Skyrim folder, where TESV.exe is.

[center]TO UNINSTALL :[/center]
just delete these files :
enbeffect.fx, enbeffectprepass.fx, enbpalette.bmp, enbseries.ini, d3d9.dll, enbbloom.fx, effect.txt.


[center]CHECK MY OTHER MODS:[/center]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7822]New Badass skull warpaint HD -MALE ONLY-[/url]
